00:08:42,594 --> 00:08:43,761
and sentimental pining.

150
00:08:43,794 --> 00:08:44,961
-Aw, shut it.

151
00:08:44,994 --> 00:08:47,727
I'm not gonna judge
myself by your standards.

152
00:08:47,761 --> 00:08:51,394
As far as I'm concerned,
it's an awesome dream.

153
00:08:51,427 --> 00:08:54,661
-I hope you're able to
get your wish someday.

154
00:08:54,694 --> 00:08:57,394
-Uh, I don't think that'll
be happening anytime soon.

155
00:09:06,161 --> 00:09:09,627
[sigh]

156
00:09:09,661 --> 00:09:11,994
-It's very rare, but
some NEXT gradually

157
00:09:12,027 --> 00:09:15,527
lose their abilities over time.

158
00:09:15,561 --> 00:09:16,027
-Mm.

159
00:09:32,594 --> 00:09:34,027
[sigh]

160
00:09:41,927 --> 00:09:42,361
Hm.

