00:10:04,694 --> 00:10:06,527
Due to the fact that
all of Benoit's targets

167
00:10:06,561 --> 00:10:09,727
have been women, he has aptly
been dubbed the Lady Killer.

168
00:10:09,761 --> 00:10:11,061
-Real charmer, huh?

