221
00:12:14,088 --> 00:12:15,755
Yes, of course.

222
00:12:15,788 --> 00:12:17,888
Ah, Yuri, my dear.

223
00:12:17,921 --> 00:12:19,155
Would you pass me the vinegar?

224
00:12:19,188 --> 00:12:21,755
I can't quite reach it.

225
00:12:21,788 --> 00:12:23,021
[chuckling]

226
00:12:23,055 --> 00:12:25,588
Don't mind Yuri, dear,
he's just rebelling a bit.

227
00:12:25,621 --> 00:12:27,955
You know, boys will be boys.

228
00:12:27,988 --> 00:12:28,921
Oh--

229
00:12:28,955 --> 00:12:30,321
[grunt]

230
00:12:30,355 --> 00:12:34,555
