through some hard times.

234
00:12:45,655 --> 00:12:47,588
He would have
eventually gone back

235
00:12:47,621 --> 00:12:50,421
to being the father
he once used to be.

236
00:12:50,455 --> 00:12:51,988
But you!

237
00:12:52,021 --> 00:12:55,821
It's all your fault!

238
00:12:55,855 --> 00:12:57,288
You!

239
00:12:57,321 --> 00:12:59,755
You!

240
00:12:59,788 --> 00:13:02,255
Why are you giving me that look?

241
00:13:02,288 --> 00:13:04,588
Are you going to kill me too?

242
00:13:04,621 --> 00:13:06,521
You're horrible!

243
00:13:06,555 --> 00:13:08,955
[scream]

244
00:13:15,255 --> 00:13:16,455
[grunt]

245
00:13:20,955 --> 00:13:24,388
[phone ringing]

246
00:13:33,388 --> 00:13:34,621
JACKSON: Over here.

247
00:13:34,655 --> 00:13:35,421
-Ah.

248
00:13:35,455 --> 00:13:36,855
-Hey.

249
00:13:36,888 --> 00:13:38,488
-Funny to see you on
this side of town.

250
00:13:38,521 --> 00:13:39,421
Heh heh.

251
00:13:39,455 --> 00:13:42,721
Uh, hey, I'll have
a Legends Cola.

252
00:13:42,755 --> 00:13:45,055
So, what'd you want
to talk to me about?

253
00:13:45,088 --> 00:13:46,188
-Brace yourself.

254
00:13:46,221 --> 00:13:47,555
I went ahead and
did some digging

255
00:13:47,588 --> 00:13:50,055
to see what I could uncover
about NEXT that might have lost

256
00:13:50,088 --> 00:13:54,221
their powers and I came
across something really big.

257
00:13:54,255 --> 00:13:56,721
-What is it?

258
00:13:56,755 --> 00:14:01,255
-Well, I hate to tell you
this, but as it turns out,

